title: S1 E8: Six Minutes of Not Telling Mom and Dad
description:
A strange encounter with their mom and dad makes Holiday and Cyrus wonder what their parents are hiding. Follow the mystery all year long..six minutes at a time.
Become a Six Minutes Superfan today! Get episodes a week early, ad free, and scripts for every episode. Show your support for the show by signing up at Patreon. https://www.patreon.com/sixminutespodcast
